Source: notify-send-ng
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Vyacheslav Levit <dev@vlevit.org>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 12),
Standards-Version: 4.5.1
Homepage: https://github.com/vlevit/notify-send-ng

Package: notify-send-ng
Architecture: all
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 notify-send.sh,
 libglib2.0-bin,
Replaces:
# /usr/bin/notify-send is replaced
 libnotify-bin,
Description: Drop-in replacement for notify-send with more features
 notify-send-ng uses notify-send.sh for updating and closing existing
 notifications, and also offers support for root users.

Package: notify-send.sh
Architecture: all
Depends:
 ${misc:Depends},
 libnotify-bin,
Description: notify-send with ability to update and close existing notifications
 notify-send.sh is a drop-in replacement for notify-send (from libnotify) with
 the ability to update and close existing notifications.
